74	- Start with an exact passage reference in this format: On: "<sentence or short passage from the draft>"
75	- Open with the single most important observation (no throat-clearing).
76	- Quote the exact sentence or short passage you are responding to; if an anchor sentence is provided, use that exact anchor.
